Package to.us.resume_builder.business.resume_file_management

Class Metadata

java.lang.Object
to.us.resume_builder.business.resume_file_management.Metadata
public class Metadata
extends java.lang.Object
This class contains metadata for a resume, such as the User attached to it and when it was created and last modified.
Author:
Jacob Curtis
